-- Bank of China Plans to Apply to Open Branch in Canada
-- B y   D o u g   A l e x a n d e r   a n d   G r e g   Q u i n n
-- 2012-05-25T18:28:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-25/bank-of-china-plans-to-apply-to-open-branch-in-canada.html
Bank of China Ltd. , the Asian
country’s third-biggest lender by assets, plans to open a branch
in  Canada .  The Beijing-based company will do business in Canada under
the name Bank of China, Toronto Branch and its principal office
will be in Markham, Ontario, according to a  notice  in the Canada
Gazette, the government’s official regulatory publication.  To contact the reporters on this story:
